casebody.data:
EX PARTE CARRINGTON No. 787,

Misc.

Decided January 12, 1970 Leon B. Polsky for Carrington. Louis J. Lefkowitz, Attorney General, Samuel A. Hirshowitz, First Assistant Attorney General, and Judith T. Younger, Assistant Attorney General, for the State of New York. Per Curiam.

The motion to dismiss is granted and the appeal is dismissed for want of jurisdiction. The petition for a writ of certiorari is denied.
